<tr>
<td rowspan="1" style="background:black;vertical-align:top;text-align:center;">
<img src="pictures/home0940.jpg" alt= " 0940" width="125px" /> 
</td>
<td style="margin-left:20px;margin-right:20px;padding:10px;padding-top:0px;vertical-align:top;">

<p align="left">This web site tells the story of a group of
interrelated printing companies and primarily records the history of Sun Engraving
and Sun Printers, industry pioneers and giants in
their field for most of the twentieth century.</p>
<p align="left">Essays, pictures,
and personal reminiscences document the companies&rsquo; significant achievements, the changing times, and many of the
experiences of the thousands of men and women who were employed
by these firms.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>

<td rowspan="1" style="background:black;">
<p align="center"><a class="greenred" style="font-size:14pt;"
href="overview.html" >Enter here</a></p>
<p align="center" style="color:white; padding:5px;">Please enable
pop-up<br /> windows before viewing the site.</p>
</td>
<td>

<p align="center" style="margin-bottom: 0">The companies were, in order of their creation:</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><br />
    Geo.W. Jones Co. (1890&ndash;1908)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Andr&eacute; &amp; Sleigh Ltd. (1893&ndash;1914)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Rembrandt Intaglio Printing Co. (1895&ndash;1932)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Anglo Engraving Co. Ltd. (1898&ndash;1914)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Mezzogravure Co. Ltd. (1910&ndash;c.1918)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Ashworth, Meredith &amp; Downer (1901&ndash;1916) </p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Menpes Printing and Engraving Co. (1908&ndash;1918)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Bushey Colour Press (1910&ndash;1914)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><b>Sun Engraving Co. Ltd.</b> (1911&ndash;1968)<br />
  Andr&eacute;, Sleigh and Anglo Ltd. (1914&ndash;18)</p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Studio Sun (1931&ndash;1951) </p>
<p align="center" style="margin-top: 0;">      Rembrandt Photogravure Ltd. (1932&ndash;1961)<br />
      <b>Sun Printers Ltd.</b> (1945&ndash;2004)</p>
